h2.heading.heading--secondary#i18n I18n and Localization

p.paragraph
  :markdown-it
    Localization information of a Datepicker instance is either retrieved global by `html[lang]` attribute
    or by default options of this jQuery Plugin.
    You can also specify individual locales with `data-locale` attribute.

    How to load locales see Moment's Docs here: http://momentjs.com/docs/#/i18n/loading-into-browser/
    For Information about available locale data see: http://momentjs.com/docs/#/i18n/locale-data/

